---
title: Nonna's Spaghetti and Turkey Meatballs with Sweet Peppers and Basil
description: Our spaghetti and meatballs taste just like Nonna's, but take a fraction of the time! The basics can be relied on tonight: hand-rolled meatballs, homemade tomato sauce, fresh basil and a sprinkle of Parmesan.
